<plot>Reformed cannibal, Bernie Grisso re-discovers his appetite after being used as a pawn in a malicious game started by his neighbor Ashley, her rotten group of friends and two sadistic cops. Armed with his legendary family's sword and a ravenous midget guardian, Grisso sets out to teach his tormentors a lesson they won't live to forget. Joe Bob Briggs, Brinke Stevens, Felissa Rose and Julie Strain join the cast in, "Evil Ever After", the ultimate fairy tale shocker.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?184733</url></doc>
